description:
DeSantis tells it like it is on Australia's covid restrictions. De Blasio: Authoritarian mandates work. Blue state covid rates rising. Clay and Buck in Alabama this weekend. Nancy Pelosi not happy. What will happen in Congress this week. Gallup: Biden down to 37% with independents. Pelosi says $4.5 trillion in spending "costs zero". Democrats don't understand basic economics.
